divs: Sighting Details a plane. The windows weren't lit up. It was so fastand totally silent. No one else was with me. I came in and told my co-workers,Pam and Chris,they laughed at me, and said "It was the space shuttle, it's suppose to land this morning." I was raised around aircraft,my dad was a flight instructor for the Air Force. For a more precise date you could look back to a night the space shuttle was landed about 5a. I can't remember an exact date. It wasn't a stealth aircraft, I've seen pictures of these. If it was an experimental aircraft of some sort, it was strange. I do live about 50 mi. south of Cape Kennedy. I never knew of this network, just found it tonight on my laptop. It disappeared over the apartment complex behind the nursing home,where I worked as a nurse,over the treetops,not seen again.
Summary: While sitting in garden area in back of Consulate Healthcare.
